# NOTE: lang-packs/ and tools/scenarios/localized/ are now COMMITTED test fixtures
# (a curated set of pack_locales + localized scenarios) so screens CI renders the
# gallery / runs runner-core-test WITHOUT the pack repo or its build toolchain. Screens
# tests presentation, not the translation corpus. Regenerate the fixtures with
# `scripts/ci/ci.sh build-fontpacks` (needs a language-packs checkout via
# $SS_LANGPACKS_REPO_DIR) + `tools/i18n/gen_localized_scenarios.py`.
# The global `*.bin` rule above would otherwise drop the fixtures' endonym_*.bin +
# runs.bin — re-include .bin files under lang-packs/ (the .ttf/.mo/manifest already commit).
!lang-packs/**/*.bin
# Throwaway shaping-spike output (regenerate: spike_shape.py -> --shape-spike ->
# spike_compare.py). Subset TTFs, run table, reference + device + diff PNGs.
tools/i18n/spike_out/
# Production-pack validation output (regenerate: validate_runs.py). Oracle +
# device PNGs diffed for the release-validation gate.
tools/i18n/validate_out/
# Throwaway scratch dir: dev screenshots, montages, zoom crops, fetched refs.
# (Was the untracked 'review/'; renamed to .tmp/ as a conventional scratch space.)
.tmp/
